Content:
We've been using Talker with our team in Minsk. It's been fantastic, some things, like JavaScript plugins are ingenious.<p>Cobbled together a plugin to auto-link FOO-1234 to our JIRA installation. Plus, multi-line pasting creates an EtherPad session.<p><pre><code>  plugin.onMessageInsertion = function(talkerEvent){
    $('td.message').replace(/(FOO-\d*)/gi, '<a href="https://foo.onjira.com/browse/+$1.toUpperCase()+ target="_blank">'+'$1'.toUpperCase()+'</a>');
    $('span.msg').replace(/(FOO-\d*)/gi, '<a href="https://foo.onjira.com/browse/+$1.toUpperCase()+ target="_blank">'+'$1'.toUpperCase()+'</a>');
  }
</code></pre>
It's a fantastic, fantastic collab tool.
